==German==

===Conjunction===
'''als''' (''subordinate clause'')

# at the same moment; [[when]] (only used in past tenses)
#:'''Als''' er ankam, öffnete sie die Tür.
#:When he arrived, she opened the door

===Adverb===
'''als'''

# [[than]]
#:2 ist größer '''als''' 1
#:2 is larger than 1
# in the function of
#:'''Als''' Polizist muss ich es tun
#:As I am a policeman, I have to do it

